*Q5. Write a SQL MERGE statement to update existing records by email, and insert if not matched.*
*Answer:*
sql
MERGE INTO target AS t
USING source AS s
ON t.email = s.email
WHEN MATCHED THEN
  UPDATE SET t.name = s.name, t.emp_id = s.emp_id
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
  INSERT (emp_id, name, email)
  VALUES (s.emp_id, s.name, s.email);


